(808, 1, '2011-01-09 06:16:49', 'task_add', 1, '{"start_date_default":"2011-01-08","end_date_default":"2011-01-08","project_id":"46","name":"RSS Feed Updates","assigned_to":"1","assign_comment":"","status":"3","priority":"3","type":"12","description":"We currently have one main AV feed setup - http:\\/\\/www.avinc.com\\/rss\\/news\\r\\n\\r\\nWe are looking to have AV video items also be added to the feed when new videos are added to the site. I don''t know if it''s possible to add only the video elements and if you had to just do all Media in general (images & videos) that would be ok too. \\r\\n\\r\\nWe are also looking to add in the AV Press Releases to this feed\\r\\nWe would also like to setup an additional feed for only UAS items (News, Press Releases, and Videos (or Media)).\\r\\n\\r\\nSome weirdness to note about the news items and feeds:\\r\\n\\r\\nThey live on two different pages (avinc.com\\/resources\\/industry & avinc.com\\/resources\\/news) there is currently an if statement in there that determines which page to link the title back to. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe TradeMark symbol does not play nice with the HTML and XML, there is currently some code in there to remove the trademark symbol before creating the title.\\r\\n\\r\\nThis is one of those situations where it started off as a simple thing and kept getting dragged out. John has been doing it in little spurts, but he''s getting really busy and I''d like to get it wrapped up for the client asap. If this all makes sense and you have the time feel free to start in on it, but if you think its going to or it starts to take more than 6 hours just give me a call and touch base. \\r\\n\\r\\nOrder of importance if things get complicated:\\r\\n\\r\\n1. Create a new RSS feed with only UAS elements (News & Press) - It would be great if at the least this could get setup. \\r\\n2. Add Press Items to AV News feed \\r\\n3. Add Videos (or all Media) - all to AV feed and only UAS ones to UAS feed","start_date":"2011-01-08 19:0