(333, 1, 'Setup Weather Widget', NULL, NULL, 83, 0, 1, '2012-03-26 20:00:00', 2012, 3, 26, 5, 1, NULL, '2012-04-01 02:00:00', 6, 100, 3, NULL, 'Setup the weather widget in the header templates', 1, 0, 0, 0, 12, 0, '2012-04-10 21:18:11', '2012-03-28 09:28:14'),
(334, 1, 'Twitter widget', NULL, NULL, 83, 0, 1, '2012-03-27 08:00:00', 2012, 3, 27, 6, 1, NULL, '2012-03-31 08:00:00', 6, 100, 3, NULL, 'Add a way to pull in the Twitter feed', 1, 0, 0, 0, 12, 0, '2012-04-10 21:18:11', '2012-03-28 09:29:03'),
(335, 1, 'Open Gallery - Membership Management', NULL, NULL, 84, 0, 1, '2012-03-28 17:00:00', 2012, 3, 28, 30, 1, NULL, '2012-04-27 02:00:00', 6, 100, 3, NULL, 'Users can register for an account (Facebook/Twitter Connect)\r\nUsers can login and add/edit up to 15 pieces of art\r\nUsers can also upload / add / delete images of themselves\r\nUser can manage all their personal info, including resetting password, etc.\r\nUser add their birthday with year to determine age for youth artists - it would also determine where the system shows their gallery (open or youth). \r\nWhen user uploads picture, depending on dimensions/size of image, certain sizes are available for sale. ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 12, 0, '2012-07-09 21:07:30', '2012-03-29 01:29:26'),
(336, 1, 'Artist Main Page', NULL, NULL, 84, 0, 1, '2012-03-29 02:00:00', 2012, 3, 28, 20, 1, NULL, '2012-04-27 02:00:00', 6, 100, 3, NULL, 'All three sections will be formatted similarly.  Each page will have thumbnails of each artist.  If you click on the thumbnail, it goes to the artist''s page where there''s information about the artist and other thumbnails of that artist''s other art pieces.  Clicking on the art thumbnail on the artists page will then allow the user to purchase the art with the current CartThrob ecommerce functionality.\r\n\r\nLayout - Similar to http://500px.com/popular where it would be 4 across and 5 rows (so a little bigger than current square images) and would display one pic of the artists gallery (their first) and have the artist name overlayed on the bottom of the pic - this would link to their artist gallery page.\r\n\r\nThis would be sorted by total meals sold from their gallery. If total meals sold is the same (i.e. 0), then the second sort value would be most recently added artists.\r\n\r\nYouth Artist Main Page - display banner with their age (under 18).', 1, 0, 0, 0, 12, 0, '2012-07-09 21:10:31', '2012-03-29 01:30:52'),
(337, 1, 'Artist Profile Gallery Page', NULL, NULL, 84, 0, 1, '2012-03-29 02:00:00', 2012, 3, 28, 20, 1, NULL, '2012-04-26 08:00:00', 6, 100, 3, NULL, 'Similar to what we have currently (i.e. http://eat-art.org/art/artist/todd_clark), but adding profile pic, and meal count badget (total meals sold from their gallery)\r\n\r\nFirst picture would be their thumbnail or cover image for the artist main page.\r\n\r\nsame layout - 5 across and 5 rows\r\n\r\nsomewhere on this page, a simple button that says flag as inappropriate  it would just email us to look at their gallery page and see if we need to delete a pic or the whole artist for spam.', 1, 0, 0, 0, 12, 0, '2012-07-09 21:11:03', '2012-03-29 01:32:09'),
(338, 1, 'Navigation Changes', NULL, NULL, 84, 0, 1, '2012-03-28 08:00:00', 2012, 3, 28, 5, 1, NULL, '2012-04-26 08:00:00', 6, 100, 3, NULL, 'Featured Artists\r\nOpen Artists\r\nYouth Art\r\nApparel', 1, 0, 0, 0, 12, 0, '2012-07-09 21:09:26', '2012-03-29 01:33:20'),
(339, 1, 'Backend Updates', NULL, NULL, 84, 0, 1, '2012-03-28 08:00:00', 2012, 3, 28, 25, 1, NULL, '2012-04-26 08:00:00', 6, 100, 3, NULL, 'Artist channel - distinguish between Artist (Open), Featured Artist, Youth Artist\r\n\r\nTotal Meal Count - automated  when purchase order is complete, update meal count (main one and artist gallery one)\r\n\r\nWe need the link of the full-res uploaded image to download and order the print in the order entry on backend so that when we go to order, it will be easily downloadable.', 1, 0, 0, 0, 12, 0, '2012-07-10 14:33:13', '2012-03-29 01:34:16'),
(340, 1, 'Google Map Integration ', NULL, NULL, 83, 0, 1, '2012-03-28 08:00:00', 2012, 3, 28, 10, 1, NULL, '2012-04-14 08:00:00', 6, 100, 3, NULL, 'see if we can feed from the address or do we need coordinates\r\nthis is needed on the individual listing pages and also a full one like on their current site:\r\nhttp://visitwesthollywood.com/maps/\r\nfigure out best way to implement either pulling directly from db or a text file', 1, 0, 0, 0, 12, 0, '2012-04-19 19:04:37', '2012-03-29 04:42:53'),
